## Step 1：Pre-flight（预检）

1. 检查当前 branch。如果在 base branch 或 repo default branch 上，**abort**：`You're on the base branch. Ship from a feature branch.`

2. 运行 `git status`（永远不要用 `-uall`）。Uncommitted changes 总是 include，无需询问。

3. 运行 `git diff <base>...HEAD --stat` 和 `git log <base>..HEAD --oneline`，理解将要 ship 的内容。

4. 检查 review readiness：

{{REVIEW_DASHBOARD}}

如果 Eng Review 不是 "CLEAR"：

打印：`No prior eng review found — ship will run its own pre-landing review in Step 9.`

检查 diff size：`git diff <base>...HEAD --stat | tail -1`。如果 diff >200 lines，补充：`Note: This is a large diff. Consider running /plan-eng-review or /autoplan for architecture-level review before shipping.`

如果缺 CEO Review，以 informational 提及（`CEO Review not run — recommended for product changes`），但不要 block。

对 Design Review：运行 `source <(~/.claude/skills/gstack/bin/gstack-diff-scope <base> 2>/dev/null)`。如果 `SCOPE_FRONTEND=true` 且 dashboard 中没有 design review（plan-design-review 或 design-review-lite），提及：`Design Review not run — this PR changes frontend code. The lite design check will run automatically in Step 9, but consider running /design-review for a full visual audit post-implementation.`（Design Review 未运行；此 PR 修改 frontend code。lite design check 会在 Step 9 自动运行，但 implementation 后可考虑运行 /design-review 做完整 visual audit。）仍然永不 block。

继续 Step 2，不要 block 或询问。Ship 会在 Step 9 运行自己的 review。

