## Step 17：Push

**Idempotency check：** 检查 branch 是否已 pushed 且 up to date。

```bash
git fetch origin <branch-name> 2>/dev/null
LOCAL=$(git rev-parse HEAD)
REMOTE=$(git rev-parse origin/<branch-name> 2>/dev/null || echo "none")
echo "LOCAL: $LOCAL  REMOTE: $REMOTE"
[ "$LOCAL" = "$REMOTE" ] && echo "ALREADY_PUSHED" || echo "PUSH_NEEDED"
```

如果 `ALREADY_PUSHED`，跳过 push，但继续 Step 18。否则用 upstream tracking push：

```bash
git push -u origin <branch-name>
```

**你还没完成。** Code 已 push，但 documentation sync 和 PR creation 是 mandatory final steps。继续 Step 18。

